metadata.title: Progress Report (2000) for Proposal "Age and growth in two deep-sea, habitat-forming  octocorallion corals in the Gulf of Alaska and Bering Sea with radiometric age validation and climate correlation"
metadata.description:

[ An NPMR project ]  [ Co-PIs: Gregor M. Cailliet, Allen H. Andrews ]
